Part A

I wanna give another experience of collecting the artworks. Like Sun Flowers from van Gogh. There are several series, and it looks fun when all of your series collected, then hunted by others in the future.

On this case, you should gather 4 pieces to make it perfectly merge. Another pieces would be appears one by one after it collected. When all of the artworks already collected, then you can say the title perfectly... its "Coronation Of The World"
